{"tid":869740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】之前放毒撚上連登恥笑 話自己塊閪可以嘟件超自信港女 原來已經復出做左","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T12:42:13.000Z","uid":204717,"like":138,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"bbba1744555014ea46b4ed0cd16b749a2f0040e9","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"話說上年有個勁撚有自信既港女<br />\n話因為有條毒撚係ig like佢啲相<br />\n就放左條毒撚上黎公審<br />\n點知連登仔唔收貨仲比起返佢底轉頭既索女ABC獸醫學生張芊穗Melissa Cheung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">詳情:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/324363/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/324363/page/1</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來已經復出左 將啲連登仔平時講話阿媽係女人既野拎出黎畫漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲做埋女權撚抨擊連登仔父權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇黎佢當年比人狙擊左十鳩幾個post條氣仲係好唔順<br />\n覺得佢笑鳩毒撚既行為無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢比人反起底都因為父權的錯! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TR1BfZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTR1BfZ2.jpg&h=ff0a43fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5XHV6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5XHV6n.jpg&h=721219cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/melibu7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmelibu7&d=615rysS2UWjGrm1Hpz%2F2dsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5b8816a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/melibu7</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7O77cX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7O77cX.jpg&h=123da6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/crazykittenpaws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcrazykittenpaws&d=615rysS2UWjGrm1Hpz%2F2dsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6f3570f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/crazykittenpaws</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LS62bBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLS62bBW.jpg&h=7b35ed91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0knbCO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0knbCO.png&h=43b40e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一次印證果班大嗌反父權平權<br />\n話男人都應該一齊加入既女權撚內心係幾撚善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我話香港好多港女真係自信到痴撚哂線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"fdfd7bfca2c069aaf03e28dd149c6a017a9b428b","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>當年金句重溫:</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cbNnFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cbNnFS.jpg&h=30aa5284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>比人like所以要放毒撚上網恥笑</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbPy2FU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbPy2FU.jpg&h=cb3c38af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>比人串鳩佢仲以為有人撐佢笑毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNLqTNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNLqTNC.jpg&h=c3e45ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>自己塊閪當八達通嘟都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"0ed83f3ea3d7ac47fea822ded3bff980fa7f61bf","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/201447_196ccaa71ca0f893d1e33a4b40ed72e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F201447_196ccaa71ca0f893d1e33a4b40ed72e8.jpg&h=f82a9a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/201228_a00a5eb049e8c88be8f7297d6c5f9e16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F201228_a00a5eb049e8c88be8f7297d6c5f9e16.jpg&h=8faf878e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/201736_2b551e19694494417853ea89f83c1408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F201736_2b551e19694494417853ea89f83c1408.jpg&h=f9f1a05d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0f9a0c0abd01447fc14b9f111ec251700aa3b8f","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/220003_e3ccf9260c62d085d5ad7668badc1229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F220003_e3ccf9260c62d085d5ad7668badc1229.jpg&h=3c5151b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/214842_3e253f4a71cf4f61b4e30268317ca5b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F214842_3e253f4a71cf4f61b4e30268317ca5b0.jpg&h=b94794bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有佢朋友認證佢係一個好有愛心<br />\n只係會笑鳩毒撚既大愛女權撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ce8faa3fc0a17744d9bcd48afd37c3b5988bca","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/201228_a00a5eb049e8c88be8f7297d6c5f9e16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F201228_a00a5eb049e8c88be8f7297d6c5f9e16.jpg&h=2cebd63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張圖說明幾多港女只係因為一副大眼con<br />\n一盒粉盒<br />\n一堆化妝品<br />\n就已經可以比同級男人自信唔知幾撚多千百萬倍<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己塊閪可以可以當八達通嘟<br />\n覺得自己可以高高在上咁笑鳩明明同自己同級數既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界真係唔痴線都唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d219085126a50897277ca280e3d97390eb7f3936","tid":869740,"uid":204717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUVnbKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUVnbKs.jpg&h=9b229ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwbUNhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwbUNhP.jpg&h=33bdff2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返自信港女啲口吻<br />\n真係完全可以想像到佢如何作為一位出色成功既女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":